<p class="">I appreciate the attitude of the right hon. Gentleman. The point I was making is that it should be safeguarded as a matter of statutory right and not be left to the discretion of a particular Home Secretary.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
