<p class="">From that, I take it that the Under-Secretary is not yet in a position to answer the question I put as to the cost to public funds of raising the pensions of existing widows during the period of three and a half years till the social insurance benefits come into effect.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
